data.description: Welcome to this stunning Victorian-style country home situated on 5.21 acres in the highly sought-after Northwest ISD. Conveniently located near HWY 114, 287, and I-35W, as well as the Alliance Shops and Restaurants, this property offers both serenity and accessibility. The home features numerous bay windows that flood the rooms with natural light, showcasing the tiled wet areas and beautiful wood floors, including the split-level stairs. The cozy living room with brick fireplace and opens to a huge side game room. Step outside and enjoy the wrap-around covered front and back porch, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings. The detached 24x30 garage with 400 sq ft of upper unfinished storage space. Updates include interior and exterior paint, an extended back patio. New pipe fencing with 3 gates, loafing shed, and a chicken coop with feed room provides space for your animals. Enjoy nights around the fire pit with seating, a charming windmill, and watch the sunset over the back pasture.
